{"type": "article", "id": 13710, "title": "自动植物栽培", "description": "", "date": "2015-08-19T07:36:14Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 33, "image": "img/article/article_show/201606061405086mGlDrNLM7O1Th8H.png", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t“Verdure” 是一个自动的植物栽培和灌溉装置，你只需要撒播种子，它便可以自行生长，自动浇水，甚至主动为自己获得光照。更重要的是，装置的底部是一个小凹槽，里面有一把小剪刀——你可以随时剪下植物来食用。你大概要问这是什么食物了，有些人爱极了但有些人觉得不可思议，这里面种植的是香菜。当然了，你也完全可以自己尝试种点儿什么别的。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141420UoQ3mO97xZ8XPj2v.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75047619\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141420Snxds8IoYGE7OJCB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.42857143\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201607261414204EiTr3qHsKbSOQeR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.47142857\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141421yFoTEcw8Uv3d0hAQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.39904762\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141422k8A1LXVt56rsPeRp.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.73714286\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}